      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;inline-math&#34;&gt;Inline Math&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Einstein&amp;rsquo;s famous equation: $E = mc^2$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;display-math&#34;&gt;Display Math&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Gaussian integral:&lt;/p&gt;
$$
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty} e^{-x^2} dx = \sqrt{\pi}
$$&lt;p&gt;Maxwell&amp;rsquo;s equations in differential form:&lt;/p&gt;
$$
\nabla \cdot \mathbf{E} = \frac{\rho}{\varepsilon_0}
$$&lt;h2 id=&#34;code-snippet&#34;&gt;Code Snippet&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
